Proposed Usage

gitignore
  - Show all commands

gitignore list
  - List all available languages

gitignore search [langage name]
  - Search for a specific language

gitignore create
  - Interactive way to generate file. 

gitignore create [languages, here, comma, separated]
  - Quick way to generate file if you know the languages

gitigore remove
  - Delete .gitignore file
